OL,8,FQuestions before standing down from
OL,9,Fthe role after five years.
OL,11,FHe delivered an emotional resignation
OL,12,Fspeech in the Senedd chamber and is
OL,13,Fset to be replaced by economy minister
OL,14,F, who was selected as the new leader
OL,15,Fof Welsh Labour on Saturday.
