OL,3,C20mph, coal tips and Calendar Girls:
OL,4,CHighlights from Mark Drakeford's final
OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,FMr took to the chamber which was in a
OL,8,Fmore jovial mood than usual at 1.30pm
OL,9,Fon a Tuesday, although serious topics
OL,10,Fincluding the conflict in the Middle
OL,11,FEast, childcare and Wales' role in the
OL,12,Fwider world were on the agenda.
OL,14,FA few moments stood out:
OL,16,FConservative MS Tom Giffard made one
OL,17,Ffinal plea with Mr to scrap the
OL,18,Fcontroversial 20mph speed limits in
OL,19,Fbuilt-up areas.
