OL,3,C20mph, coal tips and Calendar Girls:
OL,4,CHighlights from Mark Drakeford's final
OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,FThe question came following the
OL,8,Fclosing of the record-breaking
OL,9,Fpetition, which saw nearly 470,000
OL,10,Fpeople call for the policy to be
OL,11,Freversed.
OL,13,FGoSafe, which operates speed cameras
OL,14,Facross the country, has confirmed it
OL,15,Fwill increase monitoring of the speed
OL,16,Flimit from this week.
OL,18,FStronger enforcement will come in on
OL,19,Fany roads where there is evidence of
OL,20,Fsafety risks.
