OL,3,C20mph, coal tips and Calendar Girls:
OL,4,CHighlights from Mark Drakeford's final
OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,FFollowing the introduction of the
OL,8,Fcontroversial measure in September
OL,9,F2023, there had been a pause on
OL,10,Fenforcing speed limits on roads which
OL,11,Fhad recently become 20mph roads.
OL,13,FMr Giffard asked Mr : "In the last few
OL,14,Fhours your have in the job as first
OL,15,Fminister, will you make your last
OL,16,Fdecision your best one and scrap these
OL,17,F20mph speed limits?"
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/15
