OL,3,C20mph, coal tips and Calendar Girls:
OL,4,CHighlights from Mark Drakeford's final
OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,FMr responded: "I am proud that here in
OL,8,FWales, we are at the leading edge of a
OL,9,Fpolicy change that will happen far
OL,10,Fbeyond Wales.
OL,12,F"We know it's going to happen in
OL,13,FScotland. We know it happens in
OL,14,FIreland. We know that there are
OL,15,Fthousands and thousands of roads in
OL,16,FEngland which are 20mph.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/15
