OL,3,C20mph, coal tips and Calendar Girls:
OL,4,CHighlights from Mark Drakeford's final
OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,F"And the reason for that, and the
OL,8,Freason that his predecessor David
OL,9,FMelding initiated the debate on this
OL,10,Fhere on the floor of the Senedd is
OL,11,Fbecause reducing, just by a small
OL,12,Famount, the speed at which we drive in
OL,13,Fbuilt-up areas will save lives.
OL,15,F"It will save thousands and thousands
OL,16,Fof people from the trauma of being
OL,17,Fseriously injured on our roads.
OL,19,F"It gives back those roads to the
OL,20,Fpeople that live on them."
