OL,7,FLabour MS Buffy Williams asked about
OL,8,Fcoal tip safety in her constituency of
OL,9,FRhondda, to which Mr drew on his
OL,10,Fexperience of watching the Aberfan
OL,11,Fdisaster unfold as a child.
OL,13,FMr said: "Anyone brought up in the
OL,14,FLabour movement and anyone brought up
OL,15,Fin the Rhondda will be shaped by the
OL,16,Flegacy of coal mining in Wales.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/15
