OL,3,C20mph, coal tips and Calendar Girls:
OL,4,CHighlights from Mark Drakeford's final
OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,F"I vividly remember, I had just gone
OL,8,Fto secondary school in Carmarthen and
OL,9,FI returned home on an October
OL,10,Fafternoon. As I came into the house I
OL,11,Fknew something was wrong because the
OL,12,Ftelevision was on.
OL,14,F"The television was never on at that
OL,15,Ftime of the day on my house. The
OL,16,Freason the television was one was
OL,17,Fbecause the scenes from Aberfan were
OL,18,Falready being shown on it."
