OL,3,C20mph, coal tips and Calendar Girls:
OL,4,CHighlights from Mark Drakeford's final
OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,F"When that tip moved in Tylerstown in
OL,8,F2020, for anyone who saw it and
OL,9,Fcertainly for anyone lived nearby, all
OL,10,Fthose hundreds of thousands of tonnes
OL,11,Fof spoil as it moved down the mountain
OL,12,Fbrought to the surface again all those
OL,13,Fmemories.
OL,15,F"We have a programme of inspection,
OL,16,F350 inspections of the most at-risk
OL,17,Ftips in Wales this winter alone.
