OL,4,CHighlights from Mark Drakeford's final
OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,F"We have a programme of
OL,8,Finvestment...but despite Rebecca
OL,9,FEvans' (Welsh finance minister) best
OL,10,Fefforts with successive chief
OL,11,Fsecretaries to the treasury we have
OL,12,Fbeen unable to persuade the UK
OL,13,FGovernment to provide its contribution
OL,14,Fto the remediation efforts to an issue
OL,15,Fthat pre-dates devolution by many
OL,16,Fdecades."
OL,18,FConservative Samuel Kurtz MS offered
OL,19,Fup some insight into what Mr gets up
OL,20,Fto when he isn't busy being first
OL,21,Fminister.
