OL,3,C20mph, coal tips and Calendar Girls:
OL,4,CHighlights from Mark Drakeford's final
OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,FIn a question about supporting live
OL,8,Fmusic venues, Mr Kurtz revealed Mr had
OL,9,Fenjoyed one performance in particular
OL,10,Fwhile in the audience of a theatre in
OL,11,Fhis constituency.
OL,13,FMr Kurtz said: "Live music and
OL,14,Fentertainment venues are important to
OL,15,Fcultural establishments in our towns
OL,16,Fand cities, with none more important
OL,17,Fthan the Queen's Hall in Narberth.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/15
