OL,3,C20mph, coal tips and Calendar Girls:
OL,4,CHighlights from Mark Drakeford's final
OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,F"It's no secret you will soon have
OL,8,Fsome more time on your hands, first
OL,9,Fminister. What the colleagues in the
OL,10,Fchamber may not know is you've
OL,11,Factually been in the audience at the
OL,12,FQueen's Hall watching, and correct me
OL,13,Fif I'm wrong, Calendar Girls.
OL,15,F"Narberth's Queen's Hall has welcomed
OL,16,Fa number of big names in its 65-year
OL,17,Fhistory from Elton John to Wales'
OL,18,Ffinest, Goldie Lookin' Chain."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/15
