OL,3,C20mph, coal tips and Calendar Girls:
OL,4,CHighlights from Mark Drakeford's final
OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,FMr Kurtz went on to say: "Along with
OL,8,Fenjoying performances from the
OL,9,Faudience, what further support is the
OL,10,FWelsh Government providing to venues
OL,11,Fsuch as the Queen's Hall to guarantee
OL,12,Ftheir survival?"
OL,14,FMr responded as laughing was building
OL,15,Fup from the back benches of the
OL,16,Fchamber, saying: "I need to be clear
OL,17,Fthat it was a live performance of
OL,18,FCalendar Girls featuring some very
OL,19,Fbrave artists. It's not my only visit
OL,20,Fto the (Queen's) Hall and and I hope
OL,21,Fto be there again."
