OL,5,CFMQs
OL,7,FMr went on to say: "It's really
OL,8,Fimportant we have live music venues
OL,9,Fhere in Wales. The industry is under
OL,10,Fpressure. We know that."
OL,12,FThe outgoing first minister also threw
OL,13,Fthis support behind the Music Venue
OL,14,FTrust's proposal to put a small levy
OL,15,Fon the ticket price of successful live
OL,16,Fmusic businesses which will then be
OL,17,Fdistributed to smaller ones.
